            "content": "<p>Your participation in this study is entirely voluntary, and you have the right to withdraw at any time without penalty or negative consequences.<br>If you choose to withdraw, any data collected from you will be deleted and excluded from the final analysis.<br><br>The purpose of this study is to evaluate perceptions of different versions of a virtual character.<br>You will be asked to watch 17 videos featuring a virtual character and answer questions about your perception of their behavior.<br>Finally, we will collect some demographic information to ensure balanced demographic representation.<br><br>This study will take approximately 15 minutes to complete, and you will receive a compensation of $4.45.<br>The data collected in this study will be used solely for research purposes.<br><br>If you have any questions, concerns, or feedback regarding this study, please feel free to contact Lucie Galland at lucie.galland@lis-lab.fr.<br><br>Click \"Next\" to provide your consent.</p>"

